data.description: Beautifully updated contemporary home located on the 18th fairway of the Sky Mountain Golf Course. This stunning property boasts three spacious bedrooms, an inviting office space, and 2.5 well-appointed bathrooms. As you enter the large iron door, you'll be greeted by an open, modern floor plan that seamlessly blends style and functionality. The living area features large windows allowing natural light to flood in while providing unbeatable views of the picturesque golf course and surrounding mountain landscape. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with top-of-the-line appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space. It's perfect for both everyday cooking and entertaining guests. The dining area offers a cozy spot to enjoy meals while enjoying the breathtaking scenery. The master... suite is a true retreat, with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and a private golf course view. The other two bedrooms offer comfort and convenience. One of the standout features of this home is the outdoor space. Step onto the patio, and you'll find yourself in a tranquil oasis with unmatched golf course views, making it an ideal spot for relaxation or outdoor gatherings. This contemporary home is a testament to luxury living in a beautiful natural setting, and it's perfect for those who appreciate both style and the great outdoors: Clubhouse, Pool, Golf, and low HOA.
